flowRoot.flowPara: The ruby script will walk this SVG and search for layers that include the string 'plate'.
in each of this layer it looks for a text object with the label 'context' and 'icon-name'.
It then iterates throu all rect objects within that layer. It takes the dimensions of the rectangle and exports a bitmap to
Make sure you label text objects when you create new layers. Make sure your plate layers are hidden when saving.
